    <note type="biography">
        <p>Naval officer. Midshipman and mate on HMS <hi rend="italic">Beagle</hi>, 1825–36. Served off the coast of Syria, then in command of HMS <hi rend="italic">Rattler</hi> in the Burma campaign in 1852. Served off the coast of China in the 1850s, suppressing piracy, and in the Caribbean and South America before retiring in 1864.</p></note>
